Architecture Summary

TravelCopilot uses a modular Android architecture optimized for reliability and long-term maintainability.

Core Stack
Category	Technology
Language	Kotlin
UI	Jetpack Compose
Architecture	MVVM
Persistence	Room Database
DI	Hilt
Async	Coroutines + Flow
Mapping	Google Maps Compose
Voice	Android Speech APIs
Storage	DataStore
Architectural Principles
Offline-first
Voice-first
Context-aware
Reactive state management
Repository pattern
Deterministic state machines
Modular service-oriented design
High-Level Architecture
Compose UI
    ↓
ViewModels
    ↓
Core Engine Layer
    ↓
Repositories
    ↓
Room Database + DataStore
    ↓
Android Platform Services
